parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission failure can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or become unable to move, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.

symptoms: The transmission slips or fails to shift properly
the vehicle makes a rough sound
the transmission locks up or fails to accelerate.
